{"tid":1498764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"基督徒，多謝你哋！","createTime":"2019-08-23T13:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:21:58.000Z","uid":171820,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce50ebc2b803518a19debb6ece0b193f404259a","tid":1498764,"uid":171820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"利申，不以基督為恥，但係曾經以自己係香港基督徒為恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因不外乎覺得教會離地 (e.g.某教會竟然話浸禮搞唔成係仇敵興風作浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 同偽善 (e.g.傾向恐同、 認為示威者有暴力唔啱但係又對警方濫權唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n但係今晚睇見有好多基督徒一齊出嚟表態反修例，又為死傷者默哀，其實我心裏面好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n愛仇敵真係好難，特別係而家<br />\n求主幫助我哋識得點樣愛<br />\n<strong>唔係包庇過錯，而係直指其非，使其改過。</strong><br />\n<br />\n抗爭嗰度仍然漫長，希望大家繼續努力，繼續祈禱，繼續作鹽作光，願主引領<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53d8f3e1a68730be54686fac89984a8fd49de9f","tid":1498764,"uid":223966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoaOiQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoaOiQo.jpg&h=58e4930f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c159544db23c41a07fa27362f76e932ec3d726bb","tid":1498764,"uid":282583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ce50ebc2b803518a19debb6ece0b193f404259a","tid":1498764,"uid":171820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"利申，不以基督為恥，但係曾經以自己係香港基督徒為恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因不外乎覺得教會離地 (e.g.某教會竟然話浸禮搞唔成係仇敵興風作浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 同偽善 (e.g.傾向恐同、 認為示威者有暴力唔啱但係又對警方濫權唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n但係今晚睇見有好多基督徒一齊出嚟表態反修例，又為死傷者默哀，其實我心裏面好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk